## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="794f9-161">Если свойство <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A> назначено ранее созданной <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>, <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> не клонируется.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="794f9-161">When the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A> property is assigned to a previously created <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>, the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> is not cloned.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="794f9-162">Вместо этого <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A> сохраняет ссылку на ранее созданную <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="794f9-162">Instead, the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A> maintains a reference to the previously created <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="794f9-163">Если в ходе операции обновления <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A> не задана и сведения о первичном ключе находятся в <xref:System.Data.DataSet>, можно использовать класс <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder> для автоматического создания <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A>и дополнительные команды, необходимые для согласования <xref:System.Data.DataSet> с базой данных.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="794f9-163">During an update operation, if <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A> is not set and primary key information is present in the <xref:System.Data.DataSet>, you can use the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder> class to automatically generate the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A>, and additional commands needed to reconcile the <xref:System.Data.DataSet> to the database.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="794f9-164">Для этого задайте свойство <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="794f9-164">To do this, set the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> property of the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="794f9-165">Логика создания также требует, чтобы сведения о ключевом столбце присутствовали в <xref:System.Data.DataSet>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="794f9-165">The generation logic also requires key column information to be present in the <xref:System.Data.DataSet>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="794f9-166">Дополнительные сведения см. [в разделе Создание команд с помощью коммандбуилдерс](~/docs/framework/data/adonet/generating-commands-with-commandbuilders.md).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="794f9-166">For more information see [Generating Commands with CommandBuilders](~/docs/framework/data/adonet/generating-commands-with-commandbuilders.md).</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="794f9-167">В следующем примере создается <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> и задаются свойства <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> и <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="794f9-167">The following example creates an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> and sets the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> and <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A> properties.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="794f9-168">Предполагается, что вы уже создали объект <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleConnection>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="794f9-168">It assumes you have already created an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleConnection> object.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Public Shared Function CreateCustomerAdapter(conn As OracleConnection) As OracleDataAdapter   
  
  Dim da As OracleDataAdapter = New OracleDataAdapter()  
  Dim cmd As OracleCommand  
  Dim parm As OracleParameter  
  
  ' Create the SelectCommand.  
  
  cmd = New OracleCommand("SELECT * FROM Dept " & _  
                       "WHERE DName = :pDName AND Loc = :pLoc", conn)  
  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14)  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pLoc", OracleType.NVarChar, 13)  
  
  da.SelectCommand = cmd  
  
  ' Create the DeleteCommand.  
  
  cmd = New OracleCommand("DELETE FROM Dept WHERE DeptNo = :pDeptNo", conn)  
  
  parm = cmd.Parameters.Add("pDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo")  
  parm.SourceVersion = DataRowVersion.Original  
  
  da.DeleteCommand = cmd  
  
  Return da  
End Function  
```  
  
```csharp  
public static OracleDataAdapter CreateCustomerAdapter(OracleConnection conn)  
{  
  OracleDataAdapter da = new OracleDataAdapter();  
  OracleCommand cmd;  
  OracleParameter parm;  
  
  // Create the SelectCommand.  
  
  cmd = new OracleCommand("SELECT * FROM Dept " +  
                       "WHERE DName = :pDName AND Loc = :pLoc", conn);  
  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14);  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pLoc", OracleType.NVarChar, 13);  
  
  da.SelectCommand = cmd;  
  
  // Create the DeleteCommand.  
  
  cmd = new OracleCommand("DELETE FROM Dept WHERE DeptNo = :pDeptNo", conn);  
  
  parm = cmd.Parameters.Add("pDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo");  
  parm.SourceVersion = DataRowVersion.Original;  
  
  da.DeleteCommand = cmd;  
  
  return da;  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="794f9-172">Если свойство <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> назначено ранее созданному <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> объекту, <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> не клонируется.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="794f9-172">When the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> property is assigned to a previously created <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> object, the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> is not cloned.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="794f9-173">Вместо этого <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> сохраняет ссылку на ранее созданную <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="794f9-173">Instead, <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> maintains a reference to the previously created <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="794f9-174">Если в ходе операции обновления <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> не задана и сведения о первичном ключе содержатся в <xref:System.Data.DataSet>, можно использовать класс <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder> для автоматического создания <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A>и дополнительные команды, необходимые для согласования <xref:System.Data.DataSet> с базой данных.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="794f9-174">During an update operation, if <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> is not set and primary key information is present in the <xref:System.Data.DataSet>, you can use the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder> class to automatically generate <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A>, and additional commands needed to reconcile the <xref:System.Data.DataSet> to the database.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="794f9-175">Для этого задайте свойство <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="794f9-175">To do this, set the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> property of the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="794f9-176">Логика создания также требует, чтобы сведения о ключевом столбце присутствовали в <xref:System.Data.DataSet>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="794f9-176">The generation logic also requires key column information to be present in the <xref:System.Data.DataSet>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="794f9-177">Дополнительные сведения см. [в разделе Создание команд с помощью коммандбуилдерс](~/docs/framework/data/adonet/generating-commands-with-commandbuilders.md).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="794f9-177">For more information see [Generating Commands with CommandBuilders](~/docs/framework/data/adonet/generating-commands-with-commandbuilders.md).</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="794f9-178">Если выполнение этой команды возвращает строки, эти строки могут быть добавлены в <xref:System.Data.DataSet> в зависимости от того, как задано свойство <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand.UpdatedRowSource%2A> объекта <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="794f9-178">If execution of this command returns rows, these rows may be added to the <xref:System.Data.DataSet> depending upon how you set the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand.UpdatedRowSource%2A> property of the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> object.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="794f9-179">При обновлении столбца с `LONG RAW` типом данных создается исключение при вводе значения `NULL` в столбце.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="794f9-179">When you update a column with the `LONG RAW` data type, an exception is thrown when you enter a value of `NULL` in the column.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="794f9-180">Тип данных Oracle `LONG RAW` является устаревшим типом в Oracle версии 8,0.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="794f9-180">The Oracle `LONG RAW` data type is a deprecated type in Oracle version 8.0.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="794f9-181">Чтобы избежать этой ошибки, используйте `BLOB` тип данных вместо `LONG RAW`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="794f9-181">To avoid this error, use the `BLOB` data type instead of `LONG RAW`.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="794f9-182">В следующем примере создается <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> и задаются свойства <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> и <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="794f9-182">The following example creates an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> and sets the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> and <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> properties.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="794f9-183">Предполагается, что вы уже создали объект <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleConnection>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="794f9-183">It assumes you have already created an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleConnection> object.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Public Shared Function CreateCustomerAdapter(conn As OracleConnection) As OracleDataAdapter   
  
  Dim da As OracleDataAdapter = New OracleDataAdapter()  
  Dim cmd As OracleCommand  
  
  ' Create the SelectCommand.  
  
  cmd = New OracleCommand("SELECT * FROM Dept " & _  
                       "WHERE DName = :pDName AND Loc = :pLoc", conn)  
  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14)  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pLoc", OracleType.NVarChar, 13)  
  
  da.SelectCommand = cmd  
  
  ' Create the InsertCommand.  
  
  cmd = New OracleCommand("INSERT INTO Dept (DeptNo, DName) " & _  
                       "VALUES (:pDeptNo, :pDName)", conn)  
  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo")  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14, "DName")  
  
  da.InsertCommand = cmd  
  
  Return da  
End Function  
```  
  
```csharp  
public static OracleDataAdapter CreateCustomerAdapter(OracleConnection conn)  
{  
  OracleDataAdapter da = new OracleDataAdapter();  
  OracleCommand cmd;  
  
  // Create the SelectCommand.  
  
  cmd = new OracleCommand("SELECT * FROM Dept " +  
                       "WHERE DName = :pDName AND Loc = :pLoc", conn);  
  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14);  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pLoc", OracleType.NVarChar, 13);  
  
  da.SelectCommand = cmd;  
  
  // Create the InsertCommand.  
  
  cmd = new OracleCommand("INSERT INTO Dept (DeptNo, DName) " +  
                       "VALUES (:pDeptNo, :pDName)", conn);  
  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo");  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14, "DName");  
  
  da.InsertCommand = cmd;  
  
  return da;  
}  
