## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="794f9-207">Если <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> назначен ранее созданной <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>, <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> не клонируется.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="794f9-207">When <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> is assigned to a previously created <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>, the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> is not cloned.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="794f9-208">Вместо этого <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> сохраняет ссылку на ранее созданный объект <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="794f9-208">Instead, the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> maintains a reference to the previously created <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> object.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="794f9-209">Если <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> не возвращает ни одной строки, таблицы не добавляются в **набор данных**и исключение не возникает.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="794f9-209">If <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> does not return any rows, no tables are added to the **DataSet**, and no exception is raised.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="794f9-210">В следующем примере создается <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> и задаются свойства <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> и <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="794f9-210">The following example creates an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> and sets the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> and <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> properties.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="794f9-211">Предполагается, что вы уже создали объект <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleConnection>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="794f9-211">It assumes you have already created an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleConnection> object.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Public Shared Function CreateCustomerAdapter(conn As OracleConnection) As OracleDataAdapter   
  
  Dim da As OracleDataAdapter = New OracleDataAdapter()  
  Dim cmd As OracleCommand  
  
  ' Create the SelectCommand.  
  
  cmd = New OracleCommand("SELECT * FROM Dept " & _  
                       "WHERE DName = :pDName AND Loc = :pLoc", conn)  
  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14)  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pLoc", OracleType.NVarChar, 13)  
  
  da.SelectCommand = cmd  
  
  ' Create the InsertCommand.  
  
  cmd = New OracleCommand("INSERT INTO Dept (DeptNo, DName) " & _  
                       "VALUES (pDeptNo, pDName)", conn)  
  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo")  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14, "DName")  
  
  da.InsertCommand = cmd  
  
  Return da  
End Function  
```  
  
```csharp  
public static OracleDataAdapter CreateCustomerAdapter(OracleConnection conn)  
{  
  OracleDataAdapter da = new OracleDataAdapter();  
  OracleCommand cmd;  
  
  // Create the SelectCommand.  
  
  cmd = new OracleCommand("SELECT * FROM Dept " +  
                       "WHERE DName = :pDName AND Loc = :pLoc", conn);  
  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14);  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pLoc", OracleType.NVarChar, 13);  
  
  da.SelectCommand = cmd;  
  
  // Create the InsertCommand.  
  
  cmd = new OracleCommand("INSERT INTO Dept (DeptNo, DName) " +  
                       "VALUES (:pDeptNo, :pDName)", conn);  
  
